Specialist Ear care from the comfort of your own home.

Scroll to find out more

About us

With 20 years of combined experience in healthcare, we are dedicated to providing quality ear wax removal and audiology services to your home. Our team of qualified audiologists are fully registered and regulated under the BSA, HCPC & BSHAA

Why EarHealth?

  • HD Digital Otoscopy: clearly visualise and understand your diagnosis
  • Quick, Safe and painless microsuction technology
  • Mobile review of images by our ENT specialists who can offer support, advice and guidance as required.

Testimonials

"As a music teacher, my hearing is my livelihood. The expert care and advanced treatments I received at [Clinic Name] have been life-changing. Their team not only improved my hearing but also my quality of life. I'm grateful to the staff for their compassion and professionalism."

"Struggling with hearing loss for years, I felt isolated and frustrated. The specialists at [Clinic Name] were wonderful, providing me with a hearing solution that suits my lifestyle. Thanks to their care, I can now enjoy conversations with my grandchildren and participate more fully in life."

"Working in construction, I was exposed to loud noises daily, which took a toll on my hearing. The team at [Clinic Name] was phenomenal in diagnosing and treating my condition. Their personalized care and state-of-the-art technology have significantly improved my hearing and overall well-being."

"Suffering from tinnitus made my daily life and studies a struggle. The experts at [Clinic Name] provided me with effective treatment and invaluable advice on managing my condition. I'm immensely thankful for their support and the positive impact they've had on my academic and personal life."

Services we offer:

Home Ear Wax Removal

Quick, safe and painless procedure for ear cleaning, our state of the art machinery gently suctions wax from the ear

Hearing Check

Fully mobile hearing check for you at home, using 4 frequencies. Checking your hearing functionality.

ENT & Audiologist Consultation

We can securely send high resolution images and videos to your team of Audiologists and ENT specialists on hand for support and guidance when required.

Tinnitus Assessment

Troubled by tinnitus? Our expert tinnitus specialists can be on hand to diagnose and support treatment for residents.
